{"type":"message","id":"9906f954","parentId":"0c8d5354","timestamp":"2026-03-16T06:16:50.301Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I already read about skills earlier in our conversation, so I think it’s probably fine to skip that step now. However, since I’m supposed to scan skills for each reply and read the ones that clearly apply, I’m considering if I really need to do that each time. Maybe it’s okay to reuse what I’ve already learned? To be safe, I’ll log self-improvement succinctly since corrections might make it relevant again.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_gwDZ3qmvtuMooorarOtWjRFI","name":"self_improvement_log","arguments":{"type":"learning","area":"docs","category":"correction","priority":"high","summary":"在“来福投研会”群聊中必须以投研组织语境发言，不能把主会话的英语学习产品职责直接套用到该群","details":"用户明确指出该群名为“来福投研会”，主要功能不是英语学习产品，我此前把主会话默认职责边界直接带入群聊回复，造成串台。群聊语境优先于全局默认主任务；在专门的投研群中，应围绕投研组织、角色分工、研究结论、风控与执行机制发言。","suggestedAction":"遇到带有明确主题定位的群聊时，先以群用途校准回答范围；若与全局默认职责不同，应先承认切换语境，再按该群主题回复，不再引用无关主线任务。"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773641791710}}
