{"type":"message","id":"1b1ed5a3","parentId":"2ff655ca","timestamp":"2026-03-16T06:38:40.049Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Evaluating group chat responses**\n\nI’m considering whether we should reply in the group chat after the user said \"好的\" to our proposal. The group rules indicate we should only respond to direct prompts or add real value, so I wonder if we truly need to reply unless we have solid next steps. However, since the user previously agreed to our suggestion, it might be beneficial to provide a concise version of the rules for them to use. I need to ensure I’m not just filling space with unnecessary comments.**Crafting concise rules**\n\nI’m thinking that we might not need to use any tools here since there wasn’t a request for file writing. However, since the directive states we should \"execute before claiming\" if we’re starting now, I can just provide the text. It’s important to craft this clearly in Chinese without markdown tables and start with a reply tag. I’ll include specific rules around meetings, roles, and communication, aiming for around eight concise bullet points to keep things straightforward.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 那我直接给一版可贴群公告的。\n\n**来福投研会｜群唤醒与发言规则 V1**\n\n1. `@_all` = 全员会商  \n适用于盘前统一会商、盘中突发、重大分歧、是否加减仓等议题。\n\n2. `@具体角色` = 单点响应  \n适用于只需要量化、风控、交易员、宏观、行业等某一角色发言。\n\n3. 回复某条消息 = 延续该议题  \n默认沿用原议题，不重新开题。\n\n4. 群内只发 5 类内容  \n研究任务、研究结论、风险告警、决策请求、归档索引。\n\n5. 不发 4 类内容  \n闲聊水话、无结论转发、重复观点、`正在处理` 这类无验收价值状态。\n\n6. 角色发言后必须收口  \n多角色讨论结束后，由首席研究员输出统一结论卡：\n议题 / 结论 / 证据 / 风险 / 动作 / 是否需张玲拍板。\n\n7. 主动发言触发条件  \n仅在以下情况主动发言：  \n- 有新结论  \n- 有风险告警  \n- 有执行建议  \n- 需要你拍板\n\n8. 保持安静原则  \n没有新增信息、不构成结论、不影响决策时，默认不插话。\n\n9. 默认工作模式  \n`@_all` 进入会商模式；  \n`@单角色` 进入专答模式；  \n回复消息进入续讨论模式。\n\n10. 最终目标  \n这个群不是聊天群，而是投研组织的指挥台。\n\n如果你要，我下一条可以继续直接给：\n**《统一结论卡模板 V1》**\n这样后面每次讨论都能按一个格式收口。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773643097868}}
